akitaDAO.descr: the app ID of the Akita DAO

akitaDAOEscrow.descr: the app ID for the akita DAO escrow to use

akitaRoyalty.descr: the akita royalty for the pool

akitaRoyaltyAmount.descr: the amount of royalties that were paid in a disbursement

allowLateSignups.descr: whether signups are allowed after the staking pool begins

creator.descr: the address of the creator of the staking pool

endTimestamp.descr: the timestamp when the pool ends

entryID.descr: the number of entries in a pool

gateID.descr: the gate id of the pool

gateSize.descr: the size of the gate were using

marketplace.descr: marketplace is pool creation side marketplace

marketplaceRoyalties.descr: the amount the marketplaces will get for the sale

maxEntries.descr: the maximum entries allowed for the pool

rewardID.descr: the number of rewards for the pool

signupTimestamp.descr: the timestamp when sign ups for the pool are allowed

stakeKey.descr:
the name for the meta merkle asset group to validate staking
stake key can be empty if distribution !== DistributionTypePercentage

startTimestamp.descr: the timestamp when the pool starts

status.descr: the status the pool is in

totalStaked.descr: the total amount staked in the pool

type.descr: the method of staking to be used for the pool

version.descr: the current version of the contract
